#

Savory Beef and Mushroom Shepherd's Pie

$28
650 kcal

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

Comfort FoodCasseroleBeef Dish

Description

A hearty and comforting shepherd's pie filled with savory ground beef and mushrooms, topped with creamy mashed potatoes.

Ingredients

  • Ground Beef: 6 lbs
  • Mushrooms: 2 cups, diced
  • Onion: 1 large, chopped
  • Carrots: 2 cups, diced
  • Frozen Peas: 1 cup
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Beef Broth: 2 cups
  • Worcestershire Sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • Thyme: 1 teaspoon, dried
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Mashed Potatoes: 4 cups, prepared
  • Butter: 4 tablespoons
  • Milk: 1/2 cup
